text.div: • Include codes from http://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/v3-ActMood where concept is-a PRP

name: ActMoodProposal
title: ActMoodProposal
description: A non-mandated intent to perform an act. Used to record intents that are explicitly not Orders. Professional responsibility for the 'proposal' may or may not be present.
